    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>A pretty nice way to do this is to use <code>SimpleDateFormat</code>. I'll show you how:</p>\n<pre><code>SimpleDateFormat sdf = new SimpleDateFormat(&quot;d MMMM YYYY&quot;);\nDate d = new Date();\nsdf.format(d);\n</code></pre>\n<p>I see that you have the date in a variable:</p>\n<pre><code>sdf.format(variable_name);\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
