  "title" : "How can I format a &#39;LocalDate&#39; variable as a string?",
  "body" : "<p>I have a <code>LocalDate</code> variable called <code>date</code>. When I print it, it displays <code>1988-05-05</code>. I need to convert this to be printed as <code>05.May 1988</code>. How can I do this?</p>\n"
